  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. The intended use is identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Submitted under ProfileMinimal; structured Context of Use object is conveyed through the Claim and Requirement prose rather than a dedicated hasContextOfUse node.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/morrison/model/fda-centrifugal-cfd-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/morrison/data/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis",
    "https://uofa.net/morrison/data/fda-pump-cfd-outputs-mrl2"
  ],
