    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device. No critical weakeners identified. Decision recorded under ProfileMinimal; the intended use scope is described in the Claim (https://uofa.net/morrison/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case) and Requirement (https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) nodes.",
